        <p>When Can We Seek Help?
           India's mental health care landscape is changing, but more work is needed to address existing issues and provide complete, accessible care. Although anxiety is normal, if it becomes overwhelming and you have tried unsuccessfully to reduce it on your own, it may be time to seek mental health professionals through helplines or visit hospitals.</p>
